code: @Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     sourceNode.writeTo(out).     out.writeList(knownPeers). }
@Override public String toString() {     return "PeersRequest{" + "sourceNode=" + sourceNode + ", knownPeers=" + knownPeers + '}'. }

@Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o)         return true.     if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass())         return false.     PeersRequest that = (PeersRequest) o.     return Objects.equals(sourceNode, that.sourceNode) && Objects.equals(knownPeers, that.knownPeers). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(sourceNode, knownPeers). }
